sentences: Mitchel Van Dinther, better known by his stage name Jameszoo, is a record producer from 's-Hertogenbosch, Netherlands.
Dinther started as a DJ in his hometown of 's-Hertogenbosch, Netherlands.
After releasing several EPs and being signed to Brainfeeder Records, Dinther released his first full-length album Fool in May, 2016.
When discussing the balance and mixing of electronic and acoustic elements to his music, he notes Herbie Hancock and his album Sextant saying that "he completely nailed it".
